ygData.messageBody:
Yo i just made this new guild and i am looking
for cool people that want to join it and we will have
some fun with other stuff(which i haven't desided what
we would but i will find something fun). We will
make EverQuest even more famous. What ever you people
want to do is fine but If you join now you will be a
leader on another server if you are on on another
server. The Guild will be based at Freeport when i have
the money to buy a hall. The Club name is EverQuest
Server Bartoxxlous or something like that. Newbies are
welcome to join. There will also be a protection agency
and a bounty hunter agency if you want to join then
be my guest to join. The description may be bad but
it will be fun anyway. So if you want to join go
ahead.
